---
title: East Coast-Style Beef Donair with Sweet Garlic Sauce and Frites
description: Say "Hello" to the east coast with our Sweet Garlic Donair Sauce! We've drizzled it over our middle eastern spiced beef gyro, tabouli and spiced fries. Don't forget to add some fries to your pita for an extra crispy crunch!
